                            <comment id="73693" author="olivergierke" created="Mon, 12 Dec 2011 09:05:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;We&apos;re using &lt;tt&gt;ServerAddress[]&lt;/tt&gt; instead of &lt;tt&gt;List&lt;/tt&gt; in &lt;tt&gt;MongoFactoryBean&lt;/tt&gt; now and thus can register the &lt;tt&gt;PropertyEditor&lt;/tt&gt; on the array type instead of &lt;tt&gt;List&lt;/tt&gt;. This should avoid the unwanted side effects. Deployed the fix to the snapshot repo so feel free to give it a try.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
